            <cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru">
                <q>от пиршества я застал только объедки, от пива — осадки</q>
            </cit>
            <cit type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                <q>I found only leftovers from a feast, from beer — sediments</q>
            </cit>
            <bibl>
                <ref target="#src_ЮОПам."/>
                <biblScope>III 213</biblScope>
            </bibl>
        </cit>
    </cit>
    <etym xml:lang="ru">Вс. %sМиллер%s (<bibl><ref target="#ref_Вс._Миллер._ОЭ"/><biblScope>III
                151</biblScope></bibl>) сближает с <mentioned xml:lang="sa"
                    ><lang/><w>tīvra-</w><gloss><q>острый</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned
            xml:lang="sa"><w/><gloss><q>горчица</q></gloss></mentioned>, . Ср. <mentioned
            xml:lang="ps"><lang/><w>trīw</w><gloss><q>кислый</q></gloss></mentioned> (<bibl><ref
                target="#ref_Morgenstierne._EVP"/><biblScope>83</biblScope></bibl>). Случайно ли,
        однако, созвучие с <mentioned xml:lang="trk"
            ><lang/><w>čupra</w><gloss><q>гуща</q></gloss></mentioned> (<mentioned
            xml:lang="ru-x-dial"><lang/><w>чапра</w></mentioned>)? Совершенно не убедительно
        сближение с <mentioned xml:lang="grc"
            ><lang/><w>τιφος</w><gloss><q>болото</q></gloss></mentioned>
                (<bibl><author>Petersson</author><ref target="#ref_LUÅ"/><biblScope>XVI %i3%i
                69</biblScope></bibl>).</etym>
    <etym xml:lang="en">Ws. %sMiller%s (<bibl><ref target="#ref_Вс._Миллер._ОЭ"/><biblScope>III
                151</biblScope></bibl>) assimilates the word with <mentioned xml:lang="sa"
                ><lang/><w>tīvra-</w><gloss><q>spicy</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="sa"
                    ><w/><gloss><q>mustard</q></gloss></mentioned>, . Cf. <mentioned xml:lang="ps"
                ><lang/><w>trīw</w><gloss><q>sour</q></gloss></mentioned> (<bibl><ref
                target="#ref_Morgenstierne._EVP"/><biblScope>83</biblScope></bibl>). Is the
        assonance with <mentioned xml:lang="trk"
            ><lang/><w>čupra</w><gloss><q>grounds</q></gloss></mentioned> (<mentioned
            xml:lang="ru-x-dial"><lang/><w>чапра</w></mentioned>) accidental? Assimilating the word
        with <mentioned xml:lang="grc"><lang/><w>τῖφος</w><gloss><q>swamp</q></gloss></mentioned>
                (<bibl><author>Petersson</author><ref target="#ref_LUÅ"/><biblScope>XVI %i3%i
                69</biblScope></bibl>) is completely unconvincing.</etym>
</entry>
